<p><b>DEBE</b></p>
</td>
<td width="88" height="39" valign="middle">
<p><b>HABER</b></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr valign="top">
<td height="39" valign="middle">
<p>Resultado del ejercicio (129)</p>
</td>
<td width="88" height="39" valign="middle">
<p>-</p>
</td>
<td width="88" height="39" valign="middle"></td>
</tr>
<tr valign="top">
<td height="39" valign="middle">
<p>Compras y gastos (6)</p>
</td>
<td width="88" height="39" valign="middle"></td>
<td width="88" height="39" valign="middle">
